# The Most Important Architectural Principle Going Forward

## Nodes declare.

## Runtime executes.

NOT:

> nodes controlling systems directly.

That single philosophy prevents:

* spaghetti gameplay logic
* giant switch statements
* god-files
* renderer corruption
* impossible creator tooling

And it future-proofs:

* creator dashboard
* multiplayer
* cloud sync
* analytics
* sponsor overlays
* AR expansion
* procedural generation

This is the correct direction.
